summary:
Enduro is a persistent object database for Windows 8 Store Apps and .NET 4.5 applications. Enduro makes 
      modeling and accessing your persistent data very easy - almost trivial. Enduro
      is very flexible and can model any type of relationship.
      
      Enduro is built on top of a fault tolerant, ACID database engine. A crash recovery 
      mechanism is provided so that data consistency is maintained even in the event of 
      a system crash. It's the same database used by Microsoft Exchange and Active Directory.
      
      Enduro is fully async/await aware, conforming to way Store Apps are supposed to be built. 
      It is extremely performant for any application. The Enduro object store handles all update
      transparently to you, making your job easy.

      Enduro is a pure .NET 4.5 solution - no separate compilation for different platform architectures. It also conforms to the new async/await pattern required for Windows 8 Store Apps.
summary:
Enduro is a persistent object database for Windows 8 Store Apps and .NET 4.5 applications. Enduro makes 
      modeling and accessing your persistent data very easy - almost trivial. Enduro
      is very flexible and can model any type of relationship.
      
      Enduro is built on top of a fault tolerant, ACID database engine. A crash recovery 
      mechanism is provided so that data consistency is maintained even in the event of 
      a system crash. It's the same database used by Microsoft Exchange and Active Directory.
      
      Enduro is fully async/await aware, conforming to way Store Apps are supposed to be built. 
      It is extremely performant for any application. The Enduro object store handles all update
      transparently to you, making your job easy.
